  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fairy Tale Tower Defense is a 3D cartoon style tower defense game with a simple gameplay that involves utilizing resources wisely, building turrets, and then eliminating enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The health and movement speed of each monster in the game are different. When they have an energy shield, their health will increase. The pumpkin turret can deal additional damage to monsters with energy shields</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 upgradable defense turrets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 types of monsters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311220/extras/4c71c081b1452a2b329dd123505c1e81.poster.avif?t=1741584432\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311220/extras/4c71c081b1452a2b329dd123505c1e81.webm?t=1741584432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311220/extras/4c71c081b1452a2b329dd123505c1e81.mp4?t=1741584432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fairy Tale Tower Defense is a 3D cartoon style tower defense game with a simple gameplay that involves utilizing resources wisely, building turrets, and then eliminating enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The health and movement speed of each monster in the game are different. When they have an energy shield, their health will increase. The pumpkin turret can deal additional damage to monsters with energy shields</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 upgradable defense turrets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 types of monsters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311220/extras/4c71c081b1452a2b329dd123505c1e81.poster.avif?t=1741584432\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311220/extras/4c71c081b1452a2b329dd123505c1e81.webm?t=1741584432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311220/extras/4c71c081b1452a2b329dd123505c1e81.mp4?t=1741584432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
